\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus slowly became aware of his surroundings once more and sat up slowly. The ache he had felt building up in his head was gone, but he still felt more mentally drained than he had after his last nap. He could feel the waiting System notifications from his meditation training, but was a little bit wary of looking at them. He had quickly lost track of the Guide\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s instructions and had no idea if he\u8217\'92d accomplished anything more than just exhausting himself and passing out. His perception had gotten so\u8230\'85 fuzzy as his fatigue had set in that he didn\u8217\'92t trust his memories entirely. Still, he could hardly put it off forever, so he pulled them up to see how he did.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>Congratulations! Basic Meditation (Tier 2) Level 28 has evolved to Novice Meditation (Tier 3) Level 4! Wisdom has increased by 1!}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Congratulations! Novice Intuitive Problem Solving (Tier 2) Level 20 has evolved to Apprentice Intuitive Problem Solving (Tier 3) Level 1! Wisdom increased by 1!}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Congratulations! Novice Meditation (Tier 3) Level 30 has evolved to Apprentice Meditation (Tier 4) Level 1! Wisdom has increased by 1!<!$Scr_Ps::0>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 His jaw dropped open. Two meditation evolutions?! How the hell had he managed that? The Intuitive Problem Solving had to come from his inspirations on how to \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91become one with his mana\u8217\'92 and the realization that it felt like a new \u8216\'91muscle\u8217\'92\u8230\'85 He considered it for a few long moments. The first evolution had to have come when he\u8217\'92d begun to \u8216\'91dissolve\u8217\'92 himself in his mana. Then as he spread himself through his entire internal mana flow that skill must have rocketed up in levels. The second evolution had to be tied to him beginning to exercise his new control\u8230\'85 He nodded to himself. Yeah, that made the most sense based on his memories of the training. He pulled up his status to see the overall effect of the evaluation so far.}
